 brother Garry Marshall brought the pair on for an appearance on his hit TV series Happy Days, as Shirley Feeney and Laverne DeFazio, two dates for Fonzie (Henry Winkler). Cindy was married to singer Bill Hudson of musical group the Hudson Brothers from 1982 until 2000, and they shared two children, Zak and Emily Hudson. He was previously married to Goldie Hawn and is also the father of actor Kate Hudson. 